 Season 2 of “Grow Up or Nuts” is packed with more fun, thrilling and exciting moments with your favourite girls. This season, all mysteries are solved and more truths revealed. In episode 2 (Yanga Dey Pain), Kiki reveals she has commitment issues while Reki and Mudi save a client’s life. This amazing series was shot by Setwerk Films, starring Sophie Alakija-Rammal, Efe Irele, Okawa Shaznay and many others. Produced by Efe Irele and directed by Jide “J Blaze” Oyegbile. Watch the new episode below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 